  "2026-05-16T22:37:34.724Z",codex-audit,"Evidence: implemented portable builtin managed source records for bundled package alias installs, preserving local source records for explicit filesystem package paths. Verification passed: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts (47 tests); focused package install integration/unit subset; post-change dogfood passed 44 workflows; release gate passed with 1309 tests at 100 percent coverage, secret scan, npx/npm-pack/compatibility, and Sentry/telemetry gate."
